<p><b>Which software is used to solve computer problem?</b> A repair software can help you solve problems such as a slow boot, a blue screen of death, a frozen screen, or a system crash. Some of the common repair software tools include Windows Recovery Environment, System File Checker, Disk Cleanup, Disk Defragmenter, and Registry Editor.</p>
